# PHPUnit 10 conventions

- Tests at `<slug>/tests/<Class>Test.php`, namespace `<NS>\<Sub>\Tests\…`.
- `bootstrap="vendor/autoload.php"`, `failOnWarning="true"`, `cacheDirectory=".phpunit.cache"` (see `candy-core/phpunit.xml`).
- Every public method needs ≥1 test.

Patterns from `sugar-bits/tests/`, `candy-core/tests/`, `candy-sprinkles/tests/`:
- **Snapshot byte** — assert raw `\x1b[1m`-style SGR strings from `view()`. Don't abstract.
- **Snapshot cell-grid** — drive through `SugarCraft\Vt\Terminal\Terminal`, assert on `$term->screen()->cell($r,$c)`. See `candy-vt/tests/`.
- **Behaviour** — drive `update()` with scripted `KeyMsg`/`MouseMsg`, assert `[Model, ?Cmd]` tuple.
- **Coercion** — edge cases (negative/oversized index, empty, null), assert clamp/no-op matching upstream.

**Stream-write gotcha**: don't `ftruncate; rewind;` between writes. Slice deltas with `ftell`/`fseek`/`stream_get_contents` (canonical: `candy-core/tests/RendererTest.php`).

**FFI-dependent** (`candy-pty/tests/`): structural tests run unconditionally; syscall round-trips call `requirePtySyscalls()` as FIRST line and skip on FFI-less CI.

Run: `cd <slug> && composer install && vendor/bin/phpunit`.
